main event: A civilian spotted a disc-like object moving from North to South in Wantagh, New York on May 8, 1961.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 30 to 60 seconds,The sighting description included a white stripe and three lights on the underside of the object,The object oscillated up and down during the observation,No physical evidence was recorded, The conclusion of the report suggested the object was likely an aircraft.
witness description: A 15-year-old who observed the UFO while standing at an intersection.
